{"tid":2360807,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網課學習成效低 家長無奈送子女補習","createTime":"2021-01-10T06:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T11:19:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd65113b75095b080c1971eff07ff42faccbd870","tid":2360807,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T06:17:00.000Z","msg":"新蒲崗廣場有大量補習社及畫室等，成行成市，有家長帶子女出入。家長指頗為擔心疫情，但暫停面授期間，網課成效不彰，子女又無所事事，無奈送往補習中心追趕進度、充實餘暇。<br />\n<br />\n王女士送小四的女兒去功課輔導班，她認為女兒在家較懶散，難以督促，需要導師幫忙，而補習社的學習氛圍更好。她也頗擔心疫情，但知道補習社有做好防疫措施，而且是小班教學。該補習中心近月有停課幾星期，去年12月尾重開，但她不了解該補習社是否能開業。記者翻查資料，該補習社有教育局註冊，只能開放校舍作託管，不能面授。<br />\n<br />\n陳女士的女兒7歲亦到補習社上課。她同樣擔心疫情，但該補習社採取一對一上課，所以安心一點，「上網課完全學唔到嘢，一定要補習先得！」現場所見，每個學生都有獨立房間，一對一面授，而該補習社沒有註冊，可如常開業。<br />\n<br />\n興趣班教室可如常開放<br />\n興趣班教室不屬註冊教育中心，可如常開放。陳先生帶5歲的孫女學琴，孫女另外有學手工、畫畫等。他表示頗擔心疫情，因為孫女年幼，但學琴都是一對一上課，而上興趣班都會隔開坐，他有督促孫女洗手、戴口罩，所以讓她間中上興趣班，可維持學習情緒。他指琴行早前有停課兩星期，但第4波沒有停課。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/E_R4HMPKMxqObmIrsCLoew--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY5MS4y/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/PzbwUixNbgsWRGmwZ0liuA--~B/aD00MzI7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/a48117c50ec3e00b0521b2cd33817104\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FE_R4HMPKMxqObmIrsCLoew--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY5MS4y%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPzbwUixNbgsWRGmwZ0liuA--~B%2FaD00MzI7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fa48117c50ec3e00b0521b2cd33817104&h=89268cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳女士<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MYZrlo8aBIagLL8yAltcOw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/19ae71610acc0eac650740ef9ba9e754\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMYZrlo8aBIagLL8yAltcOw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F19ae71610acc0eac650740ef9ba9e754&h=ca2b79b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳先生"},{"pid":"a6d0272e1971f101a54196f9e934272fa2b20e3e","tid":2360807,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"托兒所嚟啫"},{"pid":"23e706585996a6c8c9bbff9fbcd0df40697ffe22","tid":2360807,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a6d0272e1971f101a54196f9e934272fa2b20e3e","tid":2360807,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"托兒所嚟啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"冇錯"}]}